The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Suit against Lalit Modi

Calcutta: The author of the book Social History of Indian Cricket on Tuesday filed a defamation suit in the High Court against BCCI vice-president Lalit Modi claiming one crore rupees in damages. 

In his petition, the author claimed that Modi had made caustic remarks against him for writing the book on Indian cricket. (PTI) 




